ygData.messageBody:
killed the named orc in highpass, he carries the shiny halbred, the shralok
backpack (great item and never sell it) and a totem(lore item)
just ask around in highpass for the orc camp....
oh yeah, the orc camp has the fastest spawning rate of any place in the
game...if u go either get in a group or form one..i went there at lvl 18 and
died many times in a full party of 18-23......
good luck and safe hunting
